         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">5/8/84 ¶  ¶ With best thanks, dear Mr Maiden, I beg to acknowledge the receipt of the twelve guineas draft, ¶  which has at once been forwarded to Mr Ch. Walter, whose signature has been received to t...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">84.08.05a</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">To Joseph Maiden</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">MRS 202/34, Powerhouse Museum, Sydney.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">MS is stamped and annotated '<seg>THE TECHNOLOGICAL MUSEUM | SYDNEY | No. </seg>575<seg> | RECEIVED | AUG 7 1884</seg> | Ansd. 7/8'. '<seg>SUBMITTED | 26 AUG 1884 | TO THE TRUSTEES</seg>'. </p>
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>See J. Maiden to M, 7 August <seg style="color: #000000; ">1884 (in this edition as <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>84-08-07a).</seg>
                  </p>
               </note>5/8/84</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>With best thanks, dear Mr Maiden, I beg to acknowledge the receipt of the twelve guineas draft,<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <seg style="color: #000000; ">See J. Maiden to M, 31 July 1884 (in this edition as 84-07-31b).</seg>
                  </p>
               </note> which has at once been forwarded to Mr Ch. Walter, whose signature has been received to the two vouchers, herewith returned. It was very pleasing to me, to receive the letter of acknowledgement from the trustees,<note xml:id="ftn3" type="footnote" n="3">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <seg style="color: #000000; ">
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>See Committee of Management to M, 31 July 1884 (in this edition as 84-07-31a).</seg>
                  </p>
               </note> for which I beg to render my grateful acknowledgement.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Let me advise you, to reserve of all kinds of woods, which you may get shaped for your ordinary collection, an<note xml:id="ftn4" type="footnote" n="4">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <seg style="color: #000000; ">a?</seg>
                  </p>
               </note> piece to be formed in book-pattern, as you will find that such is a <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">handy</hi>
               </seg> form to examine wood samples with readiness.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">Regardfully your</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
         </div>
      </body>
